snippet.title: The Witcher 4 - Official Reveal Trailer | The Game Awards 2024
snippet.description:
The Witcher series returns with a new protagonist. CD Projekt Red's new RPG saga replaces Geralt with Ciri as the playable character to lead us into a new fantasy saga. From the developers of The Witcher 3: Wild Hunt and Cyberpunk 2077, CDPR give us our first glimpse into the world of The Witcher 4 as Ciri takes on a fearsome monster called the Bauk in this trailer pre-rendered in a custom build of Unreal Engine 5.

#IGN #Gaming #TheGameAwards

snippet.description:
Annamalai Deepam : Karthigai Deepam - A Divine Collection of Shiva Songs
Immerse yourself in devotion with this exclusive jukebox, featuring a selection of soul-stirring songs dedicated to Lord Shiva, with special reference to the grandeur of Thiruvannamalai Annamalaiyar. Curated from Symphony‚Äôs treasure trove of superhit albums, this collection is a fitting tribute to the start of the Karthigai Deepam festival at Thiruvannamalai, heralding the ten-day-long celebration of devotion, light, and spiritual awakening.

In this Jukebox listen to

‚Ä¢ The Evergreen S.P. Balasubramaniam, whose voice echoes divinity with timeless perfection.

‚Ä¢ The Golden Honey Dripping Voice of Unnikrishnan, bringing serenity and elegance to every note.

snippet.title: Harrdy Sandhu - Tu Ru Ruu | Sagar | Bunny | Arrvindr S Khaira | Jaani | Yahvi Chavan
snippet.description:
Harrdy Sandhu returns to Desi Melodies with "Tu Ru Ruu", following smash hits like "Bijlee Bijlee" and "Titliaan." Get ready to embrace the sizzle as Harrdy unveils his sexiest avatar yet, with his sheer appeal guaranteed to overwhelm your senses.

Penned and composed by the brilliant Sagar, and elevated by Bunny‚Äôs innovative production, "Tu Ru Ruu" is a groundbreaking sonic masterpiece. The visual experience is nothing short of spectacular, with Arvvindr S Khaira pushing boundaries once again to deliver a breathtaking short film that you‚Äôll find impossible to resist rewatching in a heartbeat.

Harrdy Sandhu continues to redefine Punjabi pop music‚Äîmixing sensuality with style‚Äîand crafting a song that's as bold, hot, and unforgettable as it gets.

snippet.title: Bhanje | Lashcurry | MTV Hustle 4
snippet.description:
The track humorously advises a nephew to focus on studies, respect elders, and avoid distractions. Through sharp wordplay, it blends life lessons, authenticity, and the challenges of growing up in tough environments while showcasing resilience and ambition.

üëâ Subscribe to Saregama Music: https://bit.ly/3FkAS0W

Song Credits:
Track Name: Bhanje
Written & Performed By: Lashcurry
Music Producer: Aditya Pushkarna
Primary Artist: Lashcurry
Track Name: Bhanje
Singer/Performed By/Cast: Lashcurry
Lyricist/Written By: Lashcurry
Music Produced By: Aditya Pushkarna
Co-Composer: Aditya Pushkarna
Music Label: Saregama
Genre: Hip Hop
Sub-Genre: Rap
Language:Hindi
Country of Origin/Source: India

Lyrics:
MERE PYARE BHANJE 
JA PADHAI PE DHYAN DE
AUR FLOWS KE LIYE KABHI 
MAINE BAATEIN NAHI KARI HAIN NONSENSE 

MERE PYARE BHANJE 
JA PADHAI PE DHYAN DE
TERA VISHAY KHATAM BAS SCHOOL CHAALU
BETA CLASS MEIN BAITHA HAI SHAANT REH

LALA JAMKAR AISH KARA KAR 
ZYADA MATT AB BEHES KARA KAR 
TERE GAANO MEIN SCHOOL KA SYLLABUS 
KAALA AKSHAR BHAINS BARABAR

MARA KAS KAR EK LAGA KAR 
SO JA TU CHEHRE PE LEP LAGA KAR 
MAIDAN MEIN RAKH DIYA PAER 
BURA LAGA TUJHE THES PAHUNCHA KAR

SAB KUCH SAHI HAI BRO
AUR SAB KUCH SORTED BHI 
DEGREE WALE MERE NEECHE 
GAYA COLLEGE NAHI 
HUM HINDI WALE ACCENT KHUD KA 
MAMA NOTED PLEASE 
WOH 10 KI CHINTA NAHI MUJHE 
PATA MERI KALA HAI AUTHENTIC 

LO AA GAYA BAGHDADI KADAPI 
BAKTA NAHI BEATON PE KARTA MEIN PULL UP
AB DEKHOGE BARBADI KARWA DI 
BUDDHI GARAM DURR KARTA MEIN CHULL AB 
SHUDDHI KARAN KAROON HATT JA RE MURAKH
ULTE KARAM KARE HATYARE KHOON AB 
HUM DONO HI PANDEY MEIN CHULBUL 
AUR SAALE TU PANDEY HAI POORN AB 

MOKSH DUNGA CHHODO GHRINA
CHHAP BHI CHHOD DUNGA BOLO WAJAH 
GAAND BHI TODD DUNGA DONO TABAAH 
AREA KE COPS KARE MUJHE JAMA 
JO CALL PE CALL KARE USEY KSHAMA 
UTHATA NAHI CALL TU HO JA REH DAFA 
BOL HAI BOMB SE BAHUT HAI GAWAH
KAUN HAI GOAT TU AAJA MAIN KHADA

ISKI MASK LAGA KE 
PULL UP KARE TERE GHAR PE BANDE AADHI RAAT 
HAAN JAARI HAI GHURA-GHAARI MAARA-MAARI YAHAN BIGDE HALAAT 
PEHLE HI BOLA THA KANDHE PE SHEHER KO LAYA HOON 
 JAUN KAISE KHAALI HAATH 
MACHEGI DHOOM KAAFI
MERE SAATH MEIN DOON AUR BOOM PARTY 
DESI HOOD BAAZI POORI HARD 
MEIN DOOT NA CHOOKTA LENE SE PRAAN 

EK KANDHE PE SHAITAAN 
EK BANDE PE 6 KAAND
EK PHANDE PE BE-JAAN 
EK DHANDE MEIN LE JAAN
EK GHANTE MEIN NEPAL 
FARAARI KAAT
EK BANDE PE SEDAN SAWAARI 5
SABHI RASTE PE PEHCHAN HUMARI AAJ 

BOL MUJHE HANUMAN LAGADI AAG 
BANN-NA THA DEER CHADHA DI CAR
INDORE SE PYAAR BHEJA KARACHI PAAR (NOT SUNG)
KARA NAHI MARCH 
DANDE KE BAL PE BEHRE CHALE 
YAHAN PE ANDHE KE BAL PE NANGE BADAN JALE 
KANDE PE CHALKE THANDE BARAF SE JUNG MEIN BARASTE
GANNE KE RAS SE CHASKE TAPAKTE
JHAPKE PALAK TERI PHAT SE LAPAK LE
HAAN JHAPKE PALAK TERI PHAT SE LAPAK LE

MERE PYARE BHANJE
JA PADHAI PE DHYAN DE
MAMA DRAMA NAHI CHALEGA 
HARKATEIN KARNA SIYAAHI KE SAAMNE 

MERE AAGE NAHI 
MERE PYARE BHANJE 
JA PADHAI PE DHYAN DE 
TU CHHODEGA SOUL
